data.description: * MOTIVATED SELLER* *SQ FT 2000-2199 * PRICE REDUCTION Welcome to this gorgeous 4 bedroom, bonus room, 2 bath home Ranch style home. The home is sitting in almost 1/2 acre lot. It is conveniently located off of 101 and minutes from the famous Robbinson lake and Lake Cunningham. This unique home has many upgrades that you won't find anywhere else! New roof (2020), HVAC (2021), french drains (2021) larger septic capacity (2022) and new fenced installed (2022).   As you walk in towards the house, you'll be greeted by a cover front porsh and will go on to an open floor concept with a cathedral ceiling living room, convenient space out for any gathering. On the left you'll find the master suite with full bath, 2 sink vanity, jacuzzi tub and separate shower space to enjoy and to wind down after a long day. On the right side is where you'll find the other 3 bedrooms, the extra bonus room and the second  full bathroom   It is a double garage,  the back yard it is fenced in, you'll have plenty of space for family activities. All kitchen appliances, washer and dryer, playground convey with the property.  SELLER WILL PROFESSIONALLY CLEAN THE CARPET
